---
import Scene3D from './Scene3D';
---

<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <Scene3D client:load />
  </div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 z-10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8 animate-fade-in">
        <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full border-4 border-white/50 shadow-xl mb-6 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-50">
          <img
            src="src/assets/foto.jpeg" width="400" height="400"
            alt="Profile"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold mb-2">Lizeth Rincon</h1>
        <h2 class="text-3xl text-apple-gray-400 mb-6">Data Analyst</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xl text-apple-gray-500 mb-8 animate-slide-up">
        Los datos cuentan historias, mi trabajo es convertirlas en decisiones. 
        Soy profesional en Sistemas Computacionales con enfoque en análisis de datos, apasionada por transformar información en conocimiento útil para optimizar procesos 
        y apoyar la toma de decisiones estratégicas basadas en datos.

      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 200ms;">
      <!--
        <a href="/projects" class="bg-apple-gray-500 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-apple-gray-400 transition-colors">
          View My Work
        </a>
      -->
        <a href="#contact" class="border border-apple-gray-500 px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-apple-gray-100 transition-colors">
          Get in Touch
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/larry-xue/apple-style-portfolio" target="_blank" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
          Give me a star on GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
